channel.title: GodScape v2 Project
channel.description:
Hello, basically what i am working on is a server source.
But this is a different source....
A source like no other
A source that has everything!
Castle Wars
Deul Arena
Pest Control
Basically all the hard stuff
So i will need a team for programming this server.
[b]The Requirments[/b]
1) A rational thinker
2) Willingness to learn and teach
3) A good minded person with big dreams of a revolusion
4) Any person with a I.Q. of 40
[b]The Website[/b]
We do need forums for the server, as well as a message board for updates, ect.
[b]The Reward[/b]
The reward is the knowledge, of helping people and to be helped
[b]Thank You[/b]
This thread is open for coders and ideas, the server will be closed until complete.
If you would like to know more, contact me on MSN:
dragonfire455@yahoo.com
NOTE: Feel free to post your ideas and thoughts about this project
[b]The Developers[/b]
Hugo
dandy99
[b]The Coders[/b]
Me dandy99 Hugo
-dragonfire
